User
    ident Text
    name Text
    email Text
    password Text
    UniqueUser ident
    UniqueEmail email
    deriving Show
    deriving Eq
    deriving Read

Product
    name Text
    price Double
    productType ProductType
    deriving Show

Comment json -- Adding "json" causes ToJSON and FromJSON instances to be derived.
    message Text
    userId UserId Maybe
    deriving Eq
    deriving Show

